{"tid":1120732,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"下班被老闆任意使喚！女員工硬起來霸氣反抗　下場超悲催…","createTime":"2019-04-23T00:49:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-23T02:25:59.000Z","uid":32511,"like":37,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"6b0b556d75b378c6da9fb85e7bf39547a4eec8d7","tid":1120732,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T00:49:40.000Z","msg":"一名女網友發文抱怨，某天下班老闆突然傳來訊息，要求她立刻放下手邊的事情，幫忙跑腿把東西送到工廠，不合理的要求讓她決定硬起來反抗，沒想到換來的&hellip;竟是超悲催的下場。<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/03/25/1295808-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F03%2F25%2F1295808-XXL.jpg&h=a5be1995&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原PO在「爆怨公社」感嘆，現實生活中要遇到一位好老闆、一群好同事，真的是很不容易的事，「很多時候明明知道老闆要求過分了，或是同事推卸責任，卻也不敢吭聲，只能默默的做，但是心裡總是不平衡，就在剛剛&hellip;我試著反抗，然後我就GG了」。<br />\n <br />\n只見對話截圖中，老闆突然在下班時間傳來訊息，要求原PO把東西帶到工廠，雖然她強調自己已經離開工廠，但老闆卻回「所以我才叫你拿來工廠給我」、「在路上了嗎？我在等你，快一點」。原PO後來忍無可忍，決定霸氣喊「我已經下班了，而且我正在吃飯」，試圖做出反抗，結果反被老闆狠回「妳明天不用來了」。<br />\n <br />\n事情發展成這地步，不少網友看完紛紛留言回應「對不起笑了」、「恭喜離開爛老闆」、「記得要資遣費，順便檢舉他」、「他要的東西也可以直接丟了」、「很多老闆都喜歡下班給員工找事做，以為是奴隸啊」、「這種事本來就不是本分，只是做情分的」。"},{"pid":"c1090d5b9350e87bc79568db05e511effed675c6","tid":1120732,"uid":36296,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T01:00:11.000Z","msg":"有幾慘？"},{"pid":"579d56bb720f1e240f0f391e93b41261f019f512","tid":1120732,"uid":32588,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T01:03:49.000Z","msg":"佢炒我多謝都來唔切"},{"pid":"193c756370b5cbd8f1fe305adb5a402cd9f312ae","tid":1120732,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c1090d5b9350e87bc79568db05e511effed675c6","tid":1120732,"uid":36296,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T01:00:11.000Z","msg":"有幾慘？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T01:04:53.000Z","msg":"仲以為有咩變態野發生"},{"pid":"744709e8712b18e5f4daf605d67127443ab2339d","tid":1120732,"uid":32588,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T01:05:05.000Z","msg":"有幾悲慘，第二日老闆就會求佢返工"},{"pid":"63cc71ebf2f0a317f841a02a3144f3ec7c78b709","tid":1120732,"uid":73340,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T01:06:22.000Z","msg":"呢單直程係喜事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6750a2216877c68575fa16b093f82a20624ad442","tid":1120732,"uid":28743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T01:07:39.000Z","msg":"台灣奴性都咁重？"},{"pid":"aeb1e63a192cab1d7f386fa49114c9d7eaa518d4","tid":1120732,"uid":71913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T01:10:18.000Z","msg":"老闆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9c8ae4da7c40a824a9f058a5028a02c0cb9fd93","tid":1120732,"uid":60535,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T01:11:31.000Z","msg":"閪工唔做就唔做，驚閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e68690494d83632e7ecd80c5ff55aca6a399b36","tid":1120732,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T01:13:19.000Z","msg":"番去斬鳩個老細啦"},{"pid":"e83907a564c3909ec953f54c03d48d366cf047fd","tid":1120732,"uid":83602,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T01:17:15.000Z","msg":"solely 諗歪左 <br />\n我係壞左既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39f0785b8b9aeaabf3cc63de75ab4b09fe6d1646","tid":1120732,"uid":42435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T01:18:00.000Z","msg":"補足就走，唔通老虎下山勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77851eef73a98e1b682c8c527af1d4a0c3cbb520","tid":1120732,"uid":56323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-